text: Emily Rudd (born on February 24, 1993 in Saint Paul, Minnesota) is an American actress. She is known for her role as Nami in the Netflix live action series One Piece based on the manga by the same name. She starred in the television movie Sea Change in 2017, and the following year, in 2018, she landed small parts in programs including Philip K. Dick's Electric Dreams and the Amazon anthology series The Romanoffs. == Other websites == * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Saint Paul, Minnesota Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors
